OL,6,FA service in that handles workplace
OL,7,Fcomplaints says it has seen a 32% rise
OL,8,Fin cases since anti-discrimination
OL,9,Flaws were introduced last year.
OL,11,FStephen Glencross who heads up the
OL,12,FEmployment and Equal Opportunities
OL,13,FService explains that many of the
OL,14,Fcomplaints they receive are from
OL,15,Fpeople who may have experienced racism
OL,16,For sexism at work.
OL,18,FThey also help islanders who may have
OL,19,Fbeen unfairly dismissed or given
OL,20,Fquestionable employment contracts.
