OL,6,FNatalia Silvester, a Ukrainian-born
OL,7,Fbusiness owner who works in Guernsey,
OL,8,Fsays that she has experienced
OL,9,Fdiscrimination.
OL,11,FShe explains: "The fact that I'm a
OL,12,Ffemale in business and foreign has a
OL,13,Flot to do with it.
OL,15,F"People are very opinionated and there
OL,16,Fis a part of sexism and racism in the
OL,17,Fprofessional environment."
OL,19,FEvita Bormane is from Latvia and works
OL,20,Fin the hospitality sector.
